title: Veeam WAN Accelerators
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam WAN Accelerators via the REST API.

 It reports:
 - WAN accelerator cache size
 - High bandwidth mode status
 - Number of connection streams
 - Traffic port configuration
 - Cache folder location

 The check is informational and always returns OK if the
 WAN accelerator is found in the API response.

discovery:
 One service is created for each WAN accelerator.

item:
 The WAN accelerator name or IP address
